":116.793572,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN341521","Title":"寿县"},{"Id":"1d219dd281d8444cbf93f191c8fad5dc","Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州"},{"Id":"a9ba2d63e9354a6281cadfe0f745e377","Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州"},{"Id":"09181b60cc2b4f49b5dba7c23d46b915","Latitude":28.687675,"Longitude":115.864528,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3601","Title":"南昌"},{"Id":"cf9fa9ee51884ec99916188b47fdcd3c","Latitude":30.946576,"Longitude":118.765196,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3418","Title":"宣城"},{"Id":"c1f24100e545419694a419265e8313b6","Latitude":27.028915,"Longitude":118.311441,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN350783","Title":"建瓯"},{"Id":"11256987c4ae4e86a16bf8dfd62eb7ce","Latitude":28.687675,"Longitude":115.864528,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3601","Title":"南昌"},{"Id":"6f81f3c6f8e04391abb2670778d660e0","Latitude":31.740504,"Longitude":119.58468,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN320413","Title":"金坛"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":31.740504,"Longitude":119.58468,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN320413","Title":"金坛 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3eb8c410a52a4a0e95d2a3c56a6535fb\");'><span id='3eb8c410a52a4a0e95d2a3c56a6535fb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1182&endYear=1196')\">1182-1196年</a>，0-14岁</div><div id='3eb8c410a52a4a0e95d2a3c56a6535fb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1182&endYear=1182')\">1182年</a>，是年王遂生。上有兄王适、王逢。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1183&endYear=1186')\">1183-1186年</a>，少年居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1187&endYear=1187')\">1187年</a>，始读书，母夫人蔡氏给予幼年王遂以良好教育。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1188&endYear=1191')\">1188-1191年</a>，居乡读书。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1192&endYear=1192')\">1192年</a>，能应举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1193&endYear=1194')\">1193-1194年</a>，居乡读书。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1195&endYear=1195')\">1195年</a>，试江东，因对策抵韩侂胄而被黜落，其父万枢降一官放罢。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1196&endYear=1196')\">1196年</a>，赴省复试，径驳放。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0d40095b4b254f3abf54437230e9a95c\");'><span id='0d40095b4b254f3abf54437230e9a95c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1207')\">1205-1207年</a>，23-25岁</div><div id='0d40095b4b254f3abf54437230e9a95c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1205&endYear=1205')\">1205年4月1日</a>，父王万枢卒，丁父忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1206&endYear=1207')\">1206-1207年</a>，居家丁父忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年7月</a>，服除，居家。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"f507a233103a46aaa2051ed9613266a6\");'><span id='f507a233103a46aaa2051ed9613266a6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1224&endYear=1227')\">1224-1227年</a>，42-45岁</div><div id='f507a233103a46aaa2051ed9613266a6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1224&endYear=1224')\">1224年</a>，居家丁母忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1225&endYear=1225')\">1225年11月</a>，居家丁母忧。冬，与刘宰一起在吕城拜访魏了翁。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1226&endYear=1226')\">1226年4月</a>，四月服除，仍居家。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1227&endYear=1227')\">1227年</a>，居家。吴定夫来访。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6f81f3c6f8e04391abb2670778d660e0\");'><span id='6f81f3c6f8e04391abb2670778d660e0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1246&endYear=1248')\">1246-1248年</a>，64-66岁</div><div id='6f81f3c6f8e04391abb2670778d660e0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1246&endYear=1246')\">1246年5月</a>，五月，提举江州太平兴国宫，奉祠居乡。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1246&endYear=1246')\">1246年5月</a>，是月，增修华亭县学成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《增修华亭县学记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1247&endYear=1247')\">1247年6月</a>，奉祠居乡。六月，作《鲁公祠堂记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1247&endYear=1247')\">1247年</a>，淳安县青溪桥成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《青溪桥记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1248&endYear=1248')\">1248年</a>，除权工部尚书，未及造朝而薨。积官至龙图阁直学士通奉大夫。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.001094,"Longitude":119.846692,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN330111","Title":"富阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e9def62e5c964bea808ff368a57d2012\");'><span id='e9def62e5c964bea808ff368a57d2012_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1197&endYear=1201')\">1197-1201年</a>，15-19岁</div><div id='e9def62e5c964bea808ff368a57d2012' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1197&endYear=1197')\">1197年</a>，以父任主富阳簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1198&endYear=1198')\">1198年</a>，主富阳簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1199&endYear=1199')\">1199年</a>，主富阳簿。兄王逢登第，授溧水主簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1200&endYear=1201')\">1200-1201年</a>，主富阳簿。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d2ae751a9b914d3797ee72de6a47c78d\");'><span id='d2ae751a9b914d3797ee72de6a47c78d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1204')\">1203-1204年</a>，21-22岁</div><div id='d2ae751a9b914d3797ee72de6a47c78d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1203&endYear=1204')\">1203-1204年</a>，主富阳簿。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"83baa1f9461f4f448c9db7f125ff7fd1\");'><span id='83baa1f9461f4f448c9db7f125ff7fd1_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1201&endYear=1202')\">1201-1202年</a>，19-20岁</div><div id='83baa1f9461f4f448c9db7f125ff7fd1' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1201&endYear=1201')\">1201年10月</a>，赴京应试。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1202&endYear=1202')\">1202年3月</a>，登进士第，续任富阳主簿，刘宰作序相送。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"1d219dd281d8444cbf93f191c8fad5dc\");'><span id='1d219dd281d8444cbf93f191c8fad5dc_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1236')\">1232-1236年</a>，50-54岁</div><div id='1d219dd281d8444cbf93f191c8fad5dc' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>，迁国子监主薄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1233&endYear=1233')\">1233年</a>，又迁太常寺主薄。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1233&endYear=1233')\">1233年11月28日</a>，与洪咨夔同拜监察御史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1233&endYear=1233')\">1233年12月</a>，连上三疏，人心震悚，朝纲精明。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1234&endYear=1234')\">1234年</a>，在监察御史任上。疏奏极论进君子，退小人。论劾甚众，奸党为之一空。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1234&endYear=1234')\">1234年</a>，是年底，除右正言。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1235&endYear=1235')\">1235年</a>，寻拜殿中侍御史。劾李知孝、梁大成、莫泽。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1235&endYear=1235')\">1235年4月</a>，有跋文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《跋封事后》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1235&endYear=1235')\">1235年11月</a>，年底，除户部侍郎。辞免不允。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1236&endYear=1236')\">1236年1月</a>，正月，以户部侍郎兼同修国史、实录院同修撰，暂兼权侍左侍郎。辞免不允。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1236&endYear=1236')\">1236年4月</a>，旋以宝章阁侍制差知遂宁府，改进焕章阁待制、四川安抚制置副使兼知成都府，皆未到任。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.616272,"Longitude":119.022429,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3208","Title":"淮安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9096ce086ba9401ab2bb61147e4b2686\");'><span id='9096ce086ba9401ab2bb61147e4b2686_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年</a>，25岁</div><div id='9096ce086ba9401ab2bb61147e4b2686' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1207&endYear=1207')\">1207年11月</a>，移楚州教授。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"fbad4460714747498fe9a375565714a7\");'><span id='fbad4460714747498fe9a375565714a7_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1208&endYear=1217')\">1208-1217年</a>，26-35岁</div><div id='fbad4460714747498fe9a375565714a7' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1208&endYear=1208')\">1208年</a>，楚州教授。适苦旱，献救荒之策，参与救荒，得建康留守丘崇器重。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1209&endYear=1209')\">1209年8月</a>，参与救荒，得建康留守杨辅器重。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1210&endYear=1210')\">1210年</a>，入黄度幕。初显政治才能。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1211&endYear=1214')\">1211-1214年</a>，在黄度幕府任职。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1215&endYear=1215')\">1215年</a>，与真德秀共议救荒赈饥事，民多全活。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1216&endYear=1216')\">1216年</a>，与李道传共议救荒赈饥事，民多全活。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1217&endYear=1217')\">1217年</a>，李道传出知果州，有诗相送。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《送李果州归蜀》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送李果州归蜀（宋·王遂）<br />　　押尤韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->大原发邹鲁，功德被九州。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->迢迢数千年，伊洛乘其流。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->去之又百载，武夷阐诸幽。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->斯文代显晦，天意非人谋。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->正脉远相续，何必并世游。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->峨峨陵阳山，下镇西南陬。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->师法自心得，如亲接前修。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->一气妙亭毒，小大各有求。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->惟此生息机，不隔春与秋。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->皎皎冰雪姿，高疑揖浮丘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->太虚丽日月，纤翳无停留。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->本根自深茂，况复加穷搜。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->微言析脉理，要指会衿喉。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->工夫自中积，应物乃其优。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->汉庭高论著，周原出咨诹。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->耿耿恻隐心，若将纳诸沟。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->拳拳敬王义，敢有非嘉猷。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->俯视不义贵，如比空云浮。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->所虞素学负，岂愿清名收。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->阊阖入云端，蜀天方阻修。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->西上香炉峰，江流去悠悠。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->问学久不明，风俗日以偷。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->塞口谨勿言，令人但深忧。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->世如大膏肓，终当待公瘳。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->格天未易到，责己尤难周。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->大学无已时，白首何当休。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->陋质谢顽朽，居然费雕锼。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->建德苦不勇，怀知若为酬。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->四非去未能，用力信有由。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->永当佩深训，无作明公羞<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 同上书页四三九四</span></div></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.575549,"Longitude":118.504404,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN340521","Title":"当涂","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"75fe75f638484296a6e20f8a634b7abb\");'><span id='75fe75f638484296a6e20f8a634b7abb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1221&endYear=1223')\">1221-1223年</a>，39-41岁</div><div id='75fe75f638484296a6e20f8a634b7abb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1221&endYear=1221')\">1221年</a>，知当涂县。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1222&endYear=1222')\">1222年4月</a>，在知当涂县令任上。四月，有跋文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《跋陈少阳建炎所上第三书》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1223&endYear=1223')\">1223年</a>，在当涂令任上，有善政。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1223&endYear=1223')\">1223年12月</a>，十二月丁母忧，去当涂县令任。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"44126464980343aea3a14ec9ddd6fd3a\");'><span id='44126464980343aea3a14ec9ddd6fd3a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1227&endYear=1228')\">1227-1228年</a>，45-46岁</div><div id='44126464980343aea3a14ec9ddd6fd3a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1227&endYear=1227')\">1227年4月</a>，四月，知山阴县。刘宰有诗送行。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1228&endYear=1228')\">1228年</a>，在知山阴县任上。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":27.346635,"Longitude":117.498948,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN350781","Title":"邵武","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5ecf8d7ab35a4a64b3a8138628a2c38a\");'><span id='5ecf8d7ab35a4a64b3a8138628a2c38a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1229&endYear=1231')\">1229-1231年</a>，47-49岁</div><div id='5ecf8d7ab35a4a64b3a8138628a2c38a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1229&endYear=1229')\">1229年</a>，盗起江西、闽中，王遂陈《弭盗六策四要》，差干办审计司。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1229&endYear=1229')\">1229年12月</a>，年底知邵武军。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1230&endYear=1230')\">1230年</a>，在知邵武军任上。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>，知邵武军、兼招捕司参议官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>，辟包恢为光泽主簿。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.579375,"Longitude":116.793572,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN341521","Title":"寿县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"cf8f9f48c6c842369f3fe94028aeda88\");'><span id='cf8f9f48c6c842369f3fe94028aeda88_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1232')\">1231-1232年</a>，49-50岁</div><div id='cf8f9f48c6c842369f3fe94028aeda88' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1231&endYear=1231')\">1231年</a>，未几，罢。改知安丰军。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1232&endYear=1232')\">1232年</a>，知安丰军。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a9ba2d63e9354a6281cadfe0f745e377\");'><span id='a9ba2d63e9354a6281cadfe0f745e377_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1236&endYear=1238')\">1236-1238年</a>，54-56岁</div><div id='a9ba2d63e9354a6281cadfe0f745e377' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1236&endYear=1236')\">1236年7月9日</a>，四月，差知平江府，七月初九日到任。赴任，友人刘宰有言相送。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1236&endYear=1236')\">1236年7月</a>，上任，会两倅六邑宰，作诗劝解勤政为民。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《会平江两倅六邑宰》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">会平江两倅六邑宰（宋·王遂）<br />　　七言律诗　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->守令张官本为民，恫■<span class=\"small\">①</span>无异切吾身。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->但令六县皆朱邑，何必黄堂有信臣。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->田里要须兴孝弟，闾阎谨勿致嚬呻。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->与君共举一杯酒，化作人家点点春<span class=\"small\">②</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 疒众　② 宋史绳祖《学斋佔毕》卷三</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年2月</a>，知平江府。以秤提会子进一秩。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年3月</a>，三月，魏了翁卒。王遂经纪丧事，甚为周挚。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年7月</a>，秋七月，除敷文阁待制差知庆元府沿海制置使，改知太平州，皆未赴任。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年7月</a>，秋，有跋文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《乐庵语录》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年7月</a>，平江通判西厅记落成，有记文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《平江通判西厅记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年8月8日</a>，作文祭奠王蘋。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《祭王著作（蘋）文》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年</a>，是年，平江重修社稷坛落成，有记文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《重修社稷坛记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1237&endYear=1237')\">1237年</a>，知平江府，崇学校、宽民力、抑豪强，有善政。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1238&endYear=1238')\">1238年</a>，进显谟阁待制、知泉州，改温州，亦皆未赴任，仍知平江府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1238&endYear=1238')\">1238年8月</a>，南陵修儒学落成，请为记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《南陵修儒学记》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.687675,"Longitude":115.864528,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3601","Title":"南昌","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"09181b60cc2b4f49b5dba7c23d46b915\");'><span id='09181b60cc2b4f49b5dba7c23d46b915_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1239&endYear=1240')\">1239-1240年</a>，57-58岁</div><div id='09181b60cc2b4f49b5dba7c23d46b915' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1239&endYear=1239')\">1239年</a>，以华文阁直学士差知隆兴府兼江西转运副使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1239&endYear=1239')\">1239年4月</a>，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《题端明苏子瞻书天庆观乳泉赋后》<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题端明苏子瞻书天庆观乳泉赋后<span class=\"small\">（嘉熙三年四月旦）</span>（宋·王遂）<br />　　押尤韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->天一生兮上浮，羽人俟兮丹丘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->溯儋耳兮东注，夹昆仑兮倒流<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 明汪砢玉《珊瑚网》卷四</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1240&endYear=1240')\">1240年</a>，在知隆兴府兼江西转运副使任上。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1240&endYear=1240')\">1240年</a>，三月，溧水县小学建成，请作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《溧水县建小学记》<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"11256987c4ae4e86a16bf8dfd62eb7ce\");'><span id='11256987c4ae4e86a16bf8dfd62eb7ce_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1245&endYear=1246')\">1245-1246年</a>，63-64岁</div><div id='11256987c4ae4e86a16bf8dfd62eb7ce' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1245&endYear=1245')\">1245年</a>，复知隆兴府兼江西安抚使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1246&endYear=1246')\">1246年</a>，在知隆兴府兼江西安抚使任。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.946576,"Longitude":118.765196,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3418","Title":"宣城","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"cf9fa9ee51884ec99916188b47fdcd3c\");'><span id='cf9fa9ee51884ec99916188b47fdcd3c_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1241&endYear=1242')\">1241-1242年</a>，59-60岁</div><div id='cf9fa9ee51884ec99916188b47fdcd3c' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1241&endYear=1241')\">1241年</a>，以显谟阁待制知宁国府，政绩卓著。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1241&endYear=1241')\">1241年8月</a>，八月，作《真文忠公祠堂记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1241&endYear=1241')\">1241年9月</a>，九月，作《华亭修复经界本末记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1241&endYear=1241')\">1241年</a>，是年，作《赡学圩田记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1242&endYear=1242')\">1242年8月</a>，在知宁国府任上。秋，为刘宰《漫塘文集》作序。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《漫塘文集序》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1242&endYear=1242')\">1242年</a>，是年，作文祭梅尧臣。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《祭宛陵先生文》<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":27.028915,"Longitude":118.311441,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN350783","Title":"建瓯","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c1f24100e545419694a419265e8313b6\");'><span id='c1f24100e545419694a419265e8313b6_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1243&endYear=1244')\">1243-1244年</a>，61-62岁</div><div id='c1f24100e545419694a419265e8313b6' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1243&endYear=1243')\">1243年</a>，以宝章阁直学士知建宁府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1243&endYear=1243')\">1243年9月</a>，九月，建阳重修儒学成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《建阳重修儒学记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1243&endYear=1243')\">1243年</a>，是年，建宁府重修府学成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《建宁府重修府学记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1243&endYear=1243')\">1243年</a>，是年，建安书院成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《建安书院记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1244&endYear=1244')\">1244年</a>，知建宁府，筑风雨坛。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1244&endYear=1244')\">1244年5月5日</a>，五月，重修拱辰桥成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《重修拱辰桥记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1244&endYear=1244')\">1244年5月</a>，是月，重造十桥成，为作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《重造十桥记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1244&endYear=1244')\">1244年</a>，是年，为仁智堂作记。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《仁智堂记》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1244&endYear=1244')\">1244年</a>，是年，又作《忠列公庙碑记》<br /></div>"}],"Title":"王遂 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1182-1248)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：王可喜《王遂年谱》　录入整理：王可喜</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 5, 119.8731865, 30.870799, 10)\">0-25岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">金坛</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">富阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">富阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">金坛</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(5, 15, 118.2270705, 30.4814535, 8)\">25-58岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">淮安</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">当涂</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">金坛</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">绍兴</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">邵武</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">寿县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">苏州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">南昌</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(15, 19, 117.724604, 29.3847095, 8)\">59-66岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">宣城</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">建瓯</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">南昌</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">金坛</a></p>"}]}